This sample demostrates how to use autoconf as simple as possible.
It builds 2 applications. 
1. Application hello print "Hello World!", 
2. Application hellolib prints "Hello Lib!".

Demo features include:
1. multiple directories
2. shared library
3. release header files
4. conditional building

Manipulation
1. generate configure script
   source autogen.sh
2. clean all auto-generated files
   source clean.sh

